title: Saxon - T-Bolt (EP)2018 ak
description:
Saxon - T-Bolt (EP)2018 ak

Thunderbolt is the upcoming twenty-second studio album by British heavy metal band Saxon, due to be released on 2 February 2018. They will be touring with Black Star  Riders and supporting Judas Priest on the Firepower tour. Its gonna be the Grandfathers of Rock tour
